<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rent cars</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"
        integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA=="
        crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <style>
        .car-sec .main-sec {
            column-gap: 1cm;
        }

        .car-sec .read {
            margin: 205px;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            column-gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            row-gap: 10px;
            box-shadow: rgba(149, 157, 165, 0.473) 0px 8px 24px;
        }

        .booking-form {
            padding-top: 20px;
            width: 600px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            /* border: 1px solid darkgray; */
            box-shadow: rgba(149, 157, 165, 0.473) 0px 8px 24px;
        }

        .fs {
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 450px;
            padding: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            border-radius: 10px;

        }
        .main{display: flex;}
        .sd {
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 450px;
            padding: 20px;
            padding-top: 46px;
            justify-content: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            border-radius: 10px;

        }
       .fi{
            width: 300px;
        }
        .se{
            width: 300px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 27px;
            color: #0043ff8c;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #0043ff8c;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-bottom:10px ;
        }

        h3 {
            padding-top: 17px;
            padding-bottom: 7px;
        }

        .pick input {
            width: 90%;
            padding: 4px 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: solid 1px;
            background-color: #3a6fff29;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.749);
        }

        .pick {
            padding: 15px 30px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            row-gap: 7px;
        }

        .pick p button {
            padding: 7px 27px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: #0f4fff8c;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: whitesmoke;
        }

        .pick p {
            text-align: center;
        }

        @media (max-width:440px) {
            .car-sec .read {
                margin: 0px;
            }
            .main{
                display: inline;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <section class="car-sec">
        <div class="txt">
            <p class="txt1"> Book Your <span>
                    <%= car.name %>
                </span></p>
            <p class="txt2">Pick Up Date:<span>
                    <%= car.pdate %>
                </span> Return Date: <span>
                    <%= car.rdate %>
                </span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="main-sec">
            <div class="box">
                <img class="iii" src="<%= car.img %>" alt="">
                <div class="details">

                    <p class="car-name">
                        <%= car.name %>
                    </p>

                    <div class="review">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa-regular fa-star-half-stroke"></i>
                        <p>( <%= car.reviews %> Reviews )</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature">
                        <p><i class="fa-solid fa-chair"></i>
                            <%= car.seat %> Seat
                        </p>
                        <p><i class="fa-solid fa-gas-pump"></i>
                            <%= car.milage %>
                        </p>
                        <p><i class="fa-solid fa-car-battery"></i>
                            <%= car.battery %>
                        </p>
                        <p><i class="fa-solid fa-car-side"></i>
                            <%= car.ac %>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="price">
                        <p>₹<%= car.price %> / Day</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="booking-form">
                <h2>Book Now</h2>
                <form action="/<%= car._id %>" method="POST">
                    <div class="main">
                    <div class="fi">
                    <div class="pick">
                        <label for="name">Your Name:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Full Name" >
                    </div>
                    <div class="pick">
                        <label for="email">Your Email:</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address" >
                    </div>
                    <div class="pick">
                        <label for="Phone">Your Number:</label>
                        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="Phone number" >
                    </div>
                    <div class="pick">
                        <label for="Age">Your Birth date:</label>
                        <input type="date" id="bdate" name="bdate"  >
                    </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="se">
                    <div class="pick">
                        <label for="pan">Your Pan Number:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="pan" name="pan" placeholder="XZYEZ039V" >
                    </div>
                    <div class="pick">
                        <label for="adhar">Your Adhar Number:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="adhar" name="adhar" pattern="[0-9]{12}" placeholder="Enter 12 digits Number" >
                    </div>
                    <div class="pick">
                        <label for="Address">Your Address:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="Address" name="Address" placeholder="Address" >
                    </div>
                    <div class="pick">
                        <label for="message">Additional Message:</label>
                        <input id="message" name="message" placeholder="suggestions">
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                    <div class="pick">
                        <p><button>₹<span id="totalPrice"></span> Pay Now</button></p>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="read">

            <div class="fs">
                <h1>Read before you book!</h1>
                <h3>Local Travel</h3>
                <p class="">Cab should only be taken to places within the serviceable city. Else driver has the right to
                    deny.</p>
                <h3>Cab Category</h3>
                <p>The booking will be for cab type HATCHBACK and we do not commit on providing the preferred cab model
                    (Indica, Swift or similar)</p>
                <h3>Luggage Policy</h3>
                <p>HATCHBACK has space for 1 Luggage Bag. In case the car happens to be CNG, the luggage space will be
                    lesser. However depending on the number of passengers, luggage can be adjusted in seating area with
                    driver consent.</p>
                <h3>Driver Details</h3>
                <p>Driver details will be shared up to 30 mins prior to departure. Incase the driver/cab that reaches
                    you for pick up is different from what we have communicated, please don't board the cab and call us
                    for assistance.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="sd">
                <h3>Trip Duration</h3>
                <p>Post the package inclusions, extra Km and extra hour charges will apply as mentioned. Parking
                    charges, if applicable, should be paid to the driver directly.</p>
                <h3>Trip Time</h3>
                <p>Trip Time will be counted from the pickup time</p>
                <h3>Delays</h3>
                <p>Due to traffic or any other unavoidable reason, pickup may be delayed by 30 mins.</p>
                <h3>Charged KM</h3>
                <p>The kilometers will be charged starting from pickup location and ending at your final drop location
                </p>
                <h3>Receipts</h3>
                <p>You need to collect receipts from the driver for any extra charges paid directly to the driver during
                    the trip. MMT is not liable to provide invoices for such amounts.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </section>
    <script>
        var totalPrice =  <%=car.price%> * <%=car.day%>;
        document.getElementById("totalPrice").textContent = totalPrice;
     </script>   
</body>

</html>